# English Comments

All comments inside source files must be written in English. This applies to:

- Inline comments (`//`, `/* */`)
- JSDoc (`/** */`)
- TSDoc annotations
- Comments in CSS / SCSS / Tailwind plugin files

This rule applies regardless of the developer's native language.

## What this does NOT restrict

- User-facing text in the UI (labels, placeholders, error messages) — these may be in any language as required by the product
- Content in `*.md` documentation files — prose documentation may be in any language
